        <div class="asset-meta">
            <span class="byline">
    
                <span class="vcard author">宝徳　健</span> (<abbr class="published" title="2025-08-02T03:45:09+09:00">2025&#24180;8&#26376; 2&#26085; 03:45</abbr>)
    
            </span>

            <span class="separator">|</span> <a href="http://www.soepark.jp/soepark/2025/08/-2-104.html#comments">コメント(0)</a>
